N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 10000.5 - Amendments

State Regulations

These regulations may be amended by resolution of the board
of directors of the authority provided that the chairman, upon written notice
to the board of directors, may from time to time amend nonmaterial portions of
these regulations. Notes
